{"tid":795524,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡利奧斯離別致謝利迷：永不獨行","createTime":"2018-08-27T05:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T10:15:59.000Z","uid":122,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e01d93048ef3e18dec457956ff46d2bcbd0c06","tid":795524,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"卡利奧斯離別致謝利迷：永不獨行<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bosjxc%2FYLRYutzA32S3YvZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5afd9b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】德國門將卡利奧斯落實借用比錫達斯，臨行致謝利物浦粉絲的支持。<br />\n<br />\n卡利奧斯（Loris Karius）匆匆離開，透過Twitter表示：「很驕傲成為比錫達斯的新成員，昨日來到土耳其機場已受到熱情款待，我一定會用盡全力，協助比錫達斯爭取勝利。」<br />\n<br />\n這位德國人不忘前東家利物浦：「衷心感謝所有利迷支持，特別是一直支持我到現在的球迷，你們讓我感受到前路永遠不會獨行。」作為前德國U21代表，他由緬恩斯加盟紅軍2季，合共上陣49場。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的卡利奧斯上季歐聯決賽犯下嚴重錯誤，間接導致紅軍不敵皇家馬德里，今夏終被借到比錫達斯，為期2季，其位置被巴西門將艾利臣比加取代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錯台"},{"pid":"8afaaf0be0d22b41fb26521f3298a0b828be45f4","tid":795524,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bae0a1c5bf9a1d866d22c7a58ee79f4eaac188f6","tid":795524,"uid":89037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9087f5041d74a3abf2a76e2ca8ab3caef821a2fe","tid":795524,"uid":78873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"米仔都未走 佢就要走先 公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691a5b225eb64af73c32ce60d163f335f5ff0b52","tid":795524,"uid":4180,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9087f5041d74a3abf2a76e2ca8ab3caef821a2fe","tid":795524,"uid":78873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"米仔都未走 佢就要走先 公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj